{"prompt": "Generate a website for a video game studio. The website should be rustic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Ironclad Games</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #8B0000; /* Dark Red */\n            --secondary-color: #A0522D; /* Sienna */\n            --text-color: #FFFFFF;\n            --background-color: #2C2C2C; /* Dark Gray */\n            --accent-color: #D3D3D3; /* Light Gray */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 40px;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n            border-bottom: 5px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        main {\n            padding: 50px 20px;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(139, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(139, 0, 0, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1920x700/8B0000/FFFFFF?text=EPIC+GAMING') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            height: 70vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);\n            margin-bottom: 50px;\n            border: 10px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            line-height: 1.8;\n            max-width: 70%;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            border: 3px solid var(--primary-color);\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            border-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 60px;\n            padding: 40px;\n            background-color: rgba(44, 44, 44, 0.5); /* Slightly transparent dark gray */\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n\n        section h3 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .game-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .game-card {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            border: 2px solid var(--primary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n\n        .game-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);\n        }\n\n        .game-card img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 3px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .game-card h4 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .game-card p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .game-card .learn-more {\n            display: inline-block;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .game-card .learn-more:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n            box-shadow: 0 -4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n            border-top: 5px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        /* Simple Animation */\n        @keyframes fadeIn {\n            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }\n            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n        }\n\n        section, .game-card {\n            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out forwards;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Ironclad Games</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <main>\n        <section class=\"hero\">\n            <h2>Forge Your Legends</h2>\n            <p>Crafting immersive worlds and unforgettable adventures with passion and grit.</p>\n            <a href=\"#games\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Our Titles</a>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h3>About Us</h3>\n            <p style=\"font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.7;\">\n                Ironclad Games is a small, independent studio fueled by a love for storytelling and masterful game design. We believe in creating experiences that resonate, from the epic sweep of grand narratives to the subtle beauty of a perfectly crafted mechanic. We draw inspiration from the raw, enduring strength of iron and the rich hues of the earth.\n            </p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"games\">\n            <h3>Our Creations</h3>\n            <div class=\"game-grid\">\n                <div class=\"game-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/8B0000/FFFFFF?text=Crimson+Frontier\" alt=\"Crimson Frontier Screenshot\">\n                    <h4>Crimson Frontier</h4>\n                    <p>Embark on a perilous journey across a blood-red desert, uncovering ancient secrets and battling fearsome beasts. A tale of survival and discovery.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"learn-more\">Learn More</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"game-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/A0522D/FFFFFF?text=Stone+Heart+Saga\" alt=\"Stone Heart Saga Screenshot\">\n                    <h4>Stone Heart Saga</h4>\n                    <p>Venture into the depths of forgotten mines, where the earth's fury is unleashed. A challenging dungeon crawler with deep lore.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"learn-more\">Learn More</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"game-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/800000/FFFFFF?text=Forge+of+Dreams\" alt=\"Forge of Dreams Screenshot\">\n                    <h4>Forge of Dreams</h4>\n                    <p>Build and manage your own medieval forge, mastering the craft of blacksmithing to create legendary weapons and armor.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"learn-more\">Learn More</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h3>Get In Touch</h3>\n            <p style=\"font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.7;\">\n                Have a question or want to share your thoughts? We'd love to hear from you.\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <a href=\"mailto:contact@ironcladgames.com\" class=\"cta-button\" style=\"background-color: var(--primary-color); border-color: var(--secondary-color);\">Contact Us</a>\n            </p>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Ironclad Games. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Website crafted with dedication.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {\n            const sections = document.querySelectorAll('section');\n            sections.forEach((section, index) => {\n                section.style.animationDelay = `${index * 0.3}s`;\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}